headline: One in 4 US and UK Retailers ‘Shrouded in Supply Chain Fog,’ Avery Dennison Reports
summary: Lack of item-level visibility will hinder the industry’s adoption of technologies driving operational efficiency, Avery Dennison’s new report warns.
